# ─── .claude/ — local-only config + cached state, EXCEPT docs/ ─────
# .claude/docs/ holds contributor + AI-agent implementation
# documentation that MUST be tracked (so collaborators and future
# Claude sessions can read it). Settings, caches, and per-machine
# state stay ignored.
.claude/*
!.claude/docs/
!.claude/docs/**

# ─── iOS driver per-contributor config ─────────────────────────────
# device.env holds DEVICE_UDID / DEV_TEAM / BUNDLE_ID per contributor.
# Template committed as device.env.example; real config is local only.
native/ios-driver/device.env
native/ios-driver/AtomyxDriver.xcodeproj/

